## Basic Usage

```svelte
<script>
    import { Snap } from 'snap-ui';
</script>

<Snap.Card>
    <h3>Card Title</h3>
    <p>Your content goes here.</p>
</Snap.Card>
```

## Props

| Prop | Type | Default | Description |
|------|------|---------|-------------|
| `width` | `string` | `"100"` | Width of the card (adds "px" if not specified) |
| `height` | `string` | `"100"` | Minimum height of the card (adds "px" if not specified) |
| `bgColour` | `string` | `"ffffff"` | Background color as hex string (without #) |
| `prose` | `string` | `"false"` | Enable prose styling for rich text content ("true" or "false") |
| `children` | `Snippet` | Required | Card content |

